imdb.plot outline: Funny and uplifting comedian, producer, and author Stevie D. each week for Actors Entertainment's new talk show, The Stevie D. Show (clever title, huh?!?). Each episode, Stevie and his guests will share stories, jokes and jabs with each other. Guests include Hollywood's Hell-Raisers, and Trail-Blazers, who've all overcome adversity to become Rock Stars in their respective fields. They didn't knock on Hollywood's doors, they kicked them open. The Stevie D. Show on Actors Entertainment is on Actors Entertainment, a channel on the Actors Podcast Network, a Pepper Jay Production.
